# The harvested data IS committed (raw records + SQL databases) so the public
# data repository is self-contained and reviewable in the repo. Regenerate any
# time with:  python -m ingestion.harvest --report
#             python -m ingestion.fetch_data --api-sources
#             python -m ingestion.unify

